    "patch_code": "public Object answer(InvocationOnMock invocation) throws Throwable {\n       if (!invocation.getMethod().isAbstract()) {\n           return invocation.callRealMethod();\n       } else {\n          // Call the fallback behavior for mocking the abstract methods in the spy\n           return super.answer(invocation);\n       }\n}",
